1999/10/30  Bob Woodside  <proteus@pcnet.com>

	* FvwmIdent/FvwmIdent.h:
	* FvwmIdent/FvwmIdent.c:  Belated GSFR. This was overlooked in
	the original GSFR because it had the old flag values coded inline
	instead of relying on the header, so it never got any build
	errors when the flags were changed. (Bug Rept #499)

