	* FvwmIconMan/*.c: New config option *NoIconAction

1999-10-26  Michael Han

	* FvwmIconMan/*.c: FvwmIconam can use an alias. New resolutions: !desk, !page

1999-10-25  Hippo

	* FvwmHeme/FvwmTheme.c: Removed color leaks when changing pixmap or
	gradient.  bg and fg default to average and contrast.

