1999-08-16  Hippo

	* FvwmPager/*: new option *FvwmPagerWindow3dBorders set the pager
	mini windows to 3d if *FvwmPagerWindowColorsets is specified.
	*FvwmPagerWindowBorderWidth sets the minimum mini window size, the
	default of 1 gives the original size of 3x3.

