	reduce pipe traffic, even though I have my doubts that this module
	should be reading a config at all.  It seems to only make sense to
	control this module thru the command line.

	* FvwmRearrange/Makefile.am (FvwmTile): Make FvwmTile and FvwmCascade
	shells work.  The first 5 args must be before the -tile or -cascade.

