Thu Mar  4 00:39:15 1999  Steve Robbins  <steve@nyongwa.montreal.qc.ca>

	* FvwmIconBox/FvwmIconBox.1:
	* FvwmButtons/FvwmButtons.1:
	* FvwmBanner/FvwmBanner.c:
